name: Modern Day Mona Lisa
description: This is my personal interpretation of the modern day Mona Lisa. Handpainted with personal style using acrylic on canvas. Mona's famous face is one of the most recognized face in history, therefore i decided to take andvantage on her face to symbolize the art icon, then i stylize it with saturated color and digital-style distortion to represent the modern day i mentioned before.
